Jean Wabafiyebazu and his brother Marc were shot dead in Miami on March 30 . 
  Jean was shot in the head during a drugs raid . 
  Marc is the son of Roxanne Dube , Canada's Consul General in Miami . 
  The boys attended top private schools in Ottawa and Miami . 
  Marc has told investigators he and Jean raided homes and bought drugs in Canada . 
  He is waiting to see if he will be charged with his brother's murder . 
  Jean and Marc attended $31,000-a-year schools . 
 